I had always been a big fan of Cascarino's so I was very happy to find out that their menu at Mamma's is the same! We usually pick up but occasionally we get delivery (they're so close to us, we don't usually bother).  We've never had any issue with our orders. They have an amazing staff. Everyone is friendly and helpful. Anytime we have had people from out of town staying with us, this is our place to go! We love everything but the pizza margherita is seriously tasty. My absolute favorite pizza is the grilled chicken and mushrooms.  This place is always going to be a favorite for my family. So glad that my favorite pizza and Italian place is here to stay!
